Building Drives 




 



7
            Keys to Successful Church


Building Fund
            Capital Campaign Projects

Highlights of nationwide interviews with 15 churches that
            conducted successful building fund drives


By Brian Kluth, pastor, natl-intl 
      generosity speaker, 
      author & radio commentator (www.kluth.org)





Website Home Page


